<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem>
 <Paragraph>Formatting  of ChartAxis labels can be customized using LabelBackground,LabelForground,LabelBorderBrush,BorderBrushThickness options available.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
 <ListItem>
<Paragraph>Alignments of ChartAxis labels can be customized using LabelHorizontalAlignment and LabelVerticalAlignment with respect to LabelWidth and LabelHeight.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Prefixes and postfixes can be added to ChartAxis labels.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>ChartAxis Header text can be placed inside, outside, and across the ChartAxis</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features
</Paragraph>
<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold>LabelBackground</Bold> ColorPicker helps to set the backgound for the ChartAxis Labels.
            </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold>LabelForeground</Bold> ColorPicker helps to set the backgound for the ChartAxis Labels.
            </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold>LabelBorderBrush</Bold> ColorPicker helps to set the Border color for the ChartAxis Labels.
            </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold>LabelBorderBrushThickness</Bold> combo box helps to set the Border thickness for the ChartAxis Labels.
            </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>HeaderPosition</Bold> combo box helps to set the position of ChartArea PrimaryAxis headers.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>LabelHorizontalAlignment</Bold> combo box helps to align the ChartArea PrimaryAxis labels horizontally.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>LabelVerticalAlignment</Bold> combo box helps to align the ChartArea PrimaryAxis labels vertically.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Label Text</Bold> text box helps to set the text for the PrimaryAxis label.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>
